### Test JWT Authentication with GraphQL

# First, get a token from your Next.js frontend
# GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/token
# Authorization: Bearer <your-nextauth-session-token>

### Test GraphQL Query with JWT Authentication
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "query": "query GetMyPreferences { preferences { id user_id preferences } }"
}

